{% extends "page/page.html.twig" %}

{% block bodyClass %}bg:blue-grey-700{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <h1 class="visually-hidden">Rose Nichols, web developer</h1>
  <article class="container wl-container mar-h:auto color:off-white pad-v:18">

    <section class="mar-b:18">
      <h2 class="text:12 xl:text:14 xxl:text:16 font:500 font:rubik mar-t:none mar-b:-8 letter:s">Hi! I'm Rose</h2>

      <div class="grid l:grid-cols:5 xl:grid-cols:3 grid-gap:10 xl:grid-gap:12 xxl:grid-gap:18">
        <div class="l:grid-column-span:3 xl:grid-column-span:2">
          <p class="font:700 xl:font:400 text:2 lg:text:2 xl:text:3 line:5 mar-t:none">I'm a freelance front-end developer & designer with over {{ "now"|date("Y") - 2013 }} years' industry experience. I've worked with digital agencies, private businesses, and startups in a range of roles.</p>
          <p class="font:700 xl:font:400 lg:text:1 xl:text:2 line:8 l:line:7 xl:line:6">I'm currently based in South Wales, UK. Due to the COVID-19 pandemic, I'm only able to consider fully remote positions at this time.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="l:grid-column-span:2 xl:grid-column-span:1">
          <span class="font:rubik text:upper text:-1 letter:xl font:700">Contact details</span>
          <ul class="pad:none">
            {% set linkClasses = [
              'block',
              'pad-h:-4',
              'xl:pad-h:0',
              'pad-v:-2',
              'color:off-white',
              'bg:blue-grey-850',
              'text-dec:none',
              'text:1',
              'xl:text:2',
              'bor:2',
              'bor:blue-grey-850',
              'hover:bor:green-600',
              'focus:outline:none',
              'focus:bor:green-600',
              'active:bor:green-400',
            ] %}

            <li class="list-style:none bor-l:8 bor:blue-grey-900 hover:bor:green-600 focus-within:bor:green-600 active:bor:green-400 mar-b:-7">
              <a class="{{- linkClasses|join(' ') -}}" href="mailto:hello@rosenichols.co.uk">hello@rosenichols.co.uk</a>
            </li>
            <li class="list-style:none bor-l:8 bor:blue-grey-900 hover:bor:green-600 focus-within:bor:green-600 active:bor:green-400">
              <a class="{{- linkClasses|join(' ') -}}" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rosenicholsuk">LinkedIn</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid l:grid-cols:5 xl:grid-cols:3 grid-gap:10 xl:grid-gap:12 xxl:grid-gap:18">
      <div class="l:order:2 l:grid-column-span:3 xl:grid-column-span:2">
        <h2 class="mar-t:none mar-b:-4 text:7 font:rubik font:500 color:green-yellow-400">Do you need help with:</h2>
        <ul class="pad:none font:700 xl:font:400 text:1 xl:text:3 list-style:arrow mar-b:12">
          <li class="line:5 xl:line:4 mar-b:2 xl:mar-b:0">Production of a scaleable, fast, usable front-end interface for your application?</li>
          <li class="line:5 xl:line:4 mar-b:2 xl:mar-b:0">Refreshing the design of an old or unmaintained Drupal site?</li>
          <li class="line:5 xl:line:4 mar-b:2 xl:mar-b:0">Design and build of a new website for your small business?</li>
          <li class="line:5 xl:line:4 mar-b:2 xl:mar-b:0">Translation of design files or mockups to a functioning interface?</li>
          <li class="line:5 xl:line:4">Additional front-end capacity in your team to meet a deadline or cover an absence?</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="mar-t:none mar-b:-4 text:7 font:rubik font:500 color:green-yellow-400">I can help</h2>

        <p class="font:700 xl:font:400 text:1 xl:text:3 line:6 xl:line:5">I've specialised in front-end development and Drupal theming for over 7 years. I have a comprehensive knowledge of modern, best-practice Drupal front-end development practices. I'm also comfortable working with PHP and certain aspects of back-end Drupal development including hooks, custom modules, and Form API.</p>
        <p class="font:700 xl:font:400 text:1 xl:text:3 line:6 xl:line:5">I work well in a team, and bring a pragmatic approach to problem solving to reach workable solutions. I can follow instructions and communicate progress clearly.</p>
        <p class="font:700 xl:font:400 text:1 xl:text:3 line:6 xl:line:5">Before turning freelance, I worked for several prominent digital agencies where I led the front-end development of various projects. I provided regular updates to clients and project managers, and successfully met tight deadlines.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="order:1 l:order:none l:grid-column-span:2 xl:grid-column-span:1">
        <span class="font:rubik text:upper text:-1 letter:xl font:700">Testimonials</span>
        <ul class="pad:none">
          <li class="list-style:none bg:blue-grey-800 pad:1 line:6 mar-b:1">
            {% include 'partials/testimonial.html.twig' with {
              'body': "Rose took the lead on both the design and front-end for our platform and marketing sites, in each case taking a complex brief which underwent continual revisions and producing high quality results suited to the purpose.",
              'attribution': {
                'name': 'Charles Smith',
                'position': 'CEO',
                'company': 'Col8',
                'url': 'https://www.col8.net',
              },
            } %}
          </li>

          <li class="list-style:none bg:blue-grey-800 pad:1 line:6 mar-b:1">
            {% include 'partials/testimonial.html.twig' with {
              'body': "I've lost count of the number of projects I've worked with Rose on now. Each time, she's taken a functional but ugly interface and made it into something absolutely world-class. She uses her experience and judgement to not just build what she's been asked to, but what's best for the project. I'm looking forward to working with her again.",
              'attribution': {
                'name': 'Rupert Jabelman',
                'company': 'Jabelman Consulting',
              },
            } %}
          </li>

          <li class="list-style:none bg:blue-grey-800 pad:1 line:6">
            {% include 'partials/testimonial.html.twig' with {
              'body': "It has been a delight working with Rose. She is a conscientious, considered and knowledgeable developer, always bringing ideas to the fore and implementing them both accurately and sympathetically. Canâ€™t wait to work on a project with her again soon.",
              'attribution': {
                'name': 'Glenn Barr',
                'position': 'Scrum master',
                'company': 'Focusrite Novation',
                'url': 'https://novationmusic.com/en',
              },
            } %}
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
{% endblock %}

{% block footer_js %}
  {#<script src="/js/rtg.js"></script>#}
  <script src="/js/transform-email.js"></script>
{% endblock %}